dc_description_s: This data represents school districts for Washburn County, Wisconsin in 2021.[This data layer displays the geographic area of the School Districts within Washburn County, Wisconsin. The school district boundaries are displayed per the school district classification within the Washburn County taxroll.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://www.co.washburn.wi.us/departments/land-info-surveyor-mapping/gis-data
